ridal party, Catering Manager, and Photographer. The Master of Ceremonies will also interact with your guests, motivating them onto the dance floor to partake in all the fun.\nAs in our <em>Beyond Wedding Reception</em> package, our State-of-the-Art Sound system and special lighting deliver high quality sound and the perfect ambiance to the reception.\nPackage Includes:\n<ul>\n	<li>Disc Jockey</li>\n	<li>Master of Ceremonies</li>\n	<li>Complete Coordination of Details</li>\n	<li>5 Hours of service</li>\n	<li>State-of-the-Art Sound System</li>\n	<li>LED Lighting System with Multi-Color Dance Lighting</li>\n	<li>Wireless and wired microphones</li>\n</ul>\n<em><strong>COST: $849.99</strong></em>\n\n<br><br>\n<strong>XTREME RECEPTION:</strong><a id=\"xtremeweddingreception\" name=\"xtremeweddingreception\"></a>\nOur Xtreme Wedding Reception provides all of the services included in the Nhanced Reception and adds the following enhancements to make sure you and your guests have a memorable evening.\n<ol>\n	<li><strong>Visualization Show of Bride and Groom </strong>- A custom picture show, created from your treasured photographs that can be shown during the Cocktail Hour, Dinner Hour, or throughout the entire Reception. This service enables you to share with your guests the special memories of your courtship that brought you to this special day, adding a personal touch that will make your Reception unforgettable.</li>\n	<li><strong>Music Visualization </strong>- A visualization show of laser lights projected on a screen that complements both the music and lighting.</li>\n	<li><strong>Xtreme Lighting </strong>- 3 LED lighting systems, including a Strobe on a truss system.</li>\n	<li><strong>A second Music System</strong> - Located in the cocktail area, if separate from the reception area.</li>\n</ol>\nAs in our <em>Wedding Reception</em> packages, our State-of-the-Art Sound system and special lighting deliver high quality sound and the perfect ambiance to the reception.\nPac